 null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1000711, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O You who reveal beauty and conceal ugly things! O You who do not take a wrongdoer to task and do not tear the veil! O You who are Great Forgiver! O You who have the great forbearance! O You who have pardon abounding! O You who have opened Your hands for mercy! O Hearer of all whisperings! O You to whom all complaints are made! O Noble face! O Possessor of great favor! O You who give blessings to Your servants when they do not deserve it! O our Master! O our Lord! O our Guardian! O the Goal of our desires! I beseech You O God! not to make my being ugly with Fire.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay woh zaat jis ne neki ko zaahir kiya aur badi ko dhaanp diya aur meri pardah-daari nahi ki, ay maafi dene mein sakhi behtareen dar-guzar karne waale bohot bakhsh ne waale. Ay rehmat karne mein khule haatho’n waala, ay sar-goshi ke waqt haazir aur ay har shikaayat ke pohonchne ke maqaam, ay dar-guzar mein darya dil, ay bade ehsaan waale, ay haq-daari se pehle neymat ataa karne waale, ay paalne waale, ay sardaar, ay maalik, ay maqsood, ay faryaad-ras rehmat farma Muhammad (s.a.w.a) wa Aale Muhammad (a.s) par aur Tujh se sawaal karta hu keh mujhe Jahnnam mein na daalna.", "Urdu": "خدا کے نام سے جوبڑا رحم والا مہربان ہے اے وہ ذات جسں نے نیکی کو ظاہر کیا اور بدی کو ڈھانپ دیا اور میری پردہ دری نہیں کی اے معا فی د ینے میں سخی بہترین درگذر کرنے والے اے بہت بخشنے والے اے رحمت کرنے میں کھلے ہاتھوں والے اے سرگوشی کے وقت حاضر اور اے ہر شکایت کے پہنچنے کے مقام اے در گزر میں دریا دل اے بڑے احسان والے اے حق داری سے پہلے نعمت عطا کر دینے والے اے پالنے والے اے سردار اے مالک اے مقصود اے فریاد رس رحمت فرما محمدؐ وآل محمدؐپراورتجھ سے سوال کرتا ہوں کہ مجھے جہنم میں نہ ڈالنا۔", "RArabic": "YAA MAN AZ-HARAL JAMEELA WA SATA-RAL QABEEHA, YAA MAL-LAM YOAA-KHIZ BIL JAREE-RATE WA LAM YAHTE-KIS SITRA, YAA A’ZEE-MAL A’F-WE, YAA HASA-NAT TAJAA-WOZE, YAA WAASE-A’L MAGH-FERATE, YAA BAASE-TAL YA-DAIYNE BIR-RAHMATE, YAA SAA-HEBA KULLE NAJWAA, WA YAA MUNTA-HAA KULLE SHAK-WAA, YAA KAREE-MAS SAFHE, YAA A’ZEE-MAL MANNE, YAA MOB-TADE-AN BIN-NEA’ME QAB-LAS THE-QAAQE-HAA, YAA SAYYE-DANAA, YAA RABBA-NAA, YAA MAWLAA-NAA, YAA GHAA-YATA RAGH-BATE-NAA, AS-ALOKA YAA ALLAAHO WA AN LAA TO-SHAWWE-HO KHAL-QEE BIN-NAARE.", "ArabicText1": "یَامَنْ اَظْہَرَ الْجَمِیْلَ وَسَتَرَ الْقَبِیْحَ، یَامَنْ لَّمْ یُؤَاخِذْ بِالْجَرِیْرَۃِ وَلَمْ یَـہْـتِـکِ السِّتْرَ، یَاعَظِیْمَ الْعَفْوِ، یَاحَسَنَ التَّجَاوُزِ، یَاوَاسِعَ الْمَغْـفِـرَۃِ، یَابَاسِطَ الْیَدَیْنِ بِالرَّحْمَۃِ، یَاصَاحِبَ کُـلِّ نَجْوٰی، وَیَا مُنْتَہٰی کُلِّ شَکْوٰی، یَاکَرِیْمَ الصَّفْحِ، یَاعَظِیْمَ الْمَـنِّ، یَامُبْتَدِئًا بِالنِّعَـمِ قَبْلَ اسْـتِحْقَـاقِـہَا، یَاسَـیِّـدَنَـا، یَارَبَّـنَا، یَامَوْلَانَا، یَاغَایَۃَ رَغْـبَـتـِنَا، اَسْـاَلُـکَ یَااَللہُ وَاَنْ لَا تُـشَـوِّہُ خَـلْـقِیْ بِالـنَّـارِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSi